<refsect1 id="XS-D-1a">
<title>Example</title>
<itemizedlist mark="bullet">
  <listitem>This sample uses the DTDs generated based on FOR XML query to verify another FOR XML query result.</listitem>
  <listitem>The interface allows selection of a query for the DTD and a query for the XML document.</listitem>
  <listitem>The interface has check boxes controlling each aspect of DTD validation 
            (see the documentation about each of them).</listitem>
  <listitem>The submit button combines the DTD and the XML document, 
            verifies them and produces a result page showing the error messages.</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</refsect1>
